OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773159076
OL,3,CThree people arrested after covering
OL,4,Cbuilding in red paint
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fprotestors threw red paint over a
OL,8,Fbuilding in Manchester city centre.
OL,10,FProtesters believed to be from the
OL,11,FPeople Against Genocide group threw
OL,12,Fpaint over the windows and doors of
OL,13,FAbbey House on Booth Street on 10
OL,14,FMarch.
OL,16,FThe group said the red paint is
OL,17,Fsymbolic for the blood of lives lost
OL,18,Fon the Palestinian West Bank, Lebanon,
OL,19,Fand Iran.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
