PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773159076
OL,3,CThree people arrested after covering
OL,4,Cbuilding in red paint
OL,6,FTwo demonstrators were then pictured
OL,7,Fsitting on top of the entrance roof to
OL,8,Fthe building, which sits on the
OL,9,Fjunction with Mosley Street.
OL,11,FA police cordon was put in place
OL,12,Faround the building as emergency
OL,13,Fservices attended the scene.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,16,FPolice has confirmed that three
OL,17,Farrests have been made in connection
OL,18,Fwith the protest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
