PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773159076
OL,3,CThree people arrested after covering
OL,4,Cbuilding in red paint
OL,6,FA man, 25, and two women, in their
OL,7,Fearly 20s, have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of criminal damage, GMP said.
OL,10,FThe force spokesperson added that
OL,11,Fspecialist officers remain on the
OL,12,Fscene while "efforts to bring the
OL,13,Fprotest activity to a safe conclusion
OL,14,Fremain ongoing".
OL,16,FThe protesters have targeted Abbey
OL,17,FHouse as a company linked to Elbit
OL,18,FSystems, an Israeli arms firm, is
OL,19,Fbased there, the campaign group said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
