PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773159076
OL,3,CThree people arrested after covering
OL,4,Cbuilding in red paint
OL,6,FIn a statement, GMP said: "At around
OL,7,F6.55am this morning, we were called to
OL,8,Fan ongoing disturbance on Nicholas
OL,9,FStreet in the city centre.
OL,11,F"Officers attended the scene and
OL,12,Farrested a man aged 25 on suspicion of
OL,13,Fpublic order and two women in their
OL,14,Fearly twenties on suspicion of
OL,15,Fcriminal damage.
OL,17,F"Specialist Police Resources remain at
OL,18,Fthe scene whilst efforts to bring the
OL,19,Fprotest activity to a safe conclusion
OL,20,Fremain ongoing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
